QueryText: how to increase yield of paddy
How to control flower drop problem in brinjal crop?
KCCAns: Spray Planofix 4 to 5 Ml at 15 liter of water.

QueryText: How to control Blast disease in paddy crop ?
KCCAns: Spray Tricyclazol, hexacorazol, propiconazol 20-25 ml per pump and steptrocyclin 2 to 3 gram per pump.
